  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was listening to it, and they have many other songs which were made so popular with the people and with the [INAUDIBLE] who believed and those who did not believe but were convinced here is something well going on for the German people because they came after a very devastating period of time of high inflation.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were-- kind of felt as rescued by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family-- you see, they tried to make our life as bearable as possible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think that they ever-- I did not feel that ever tied to hem and haw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are in immediate danger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, while the years progressed, of course this came into [? fall. ?] But at that time, speaking of 1933, 1934, 1935, it was not yet a-- a strong a factor that our-- my family-- and my family was very big.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sisters, who-- my brother was born two and a half years later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then came Miriam, and I have pictures, which I would like later to show you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then came Miriam, and then came Rosa, so it was obviously a feeling of well-being, of still well-being with a natural continuation of life, without knowing the great danger standing ahead, or being ahead.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a very good question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews-- I remember my father had meetings in our-- arranged in our house, and they already touched on something like-- like possible emigration, and this was sent to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but it was so costly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As far as I remember, those who could show a 20,000 pounds and could show that they will not be a kind of burden to the man that would get a-- what they called at that time a certificate, Zertifikat, and could auswandern, could go.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
